*** Version 6 ***
- added the possibility to pass a stream-socket-like object to the constructor
- when receiving data from the socket, it's now checked whether the recv() call returned data or not


*** Version 5 ***
- added manual garbage collection in places where lots of unnecessary data might persist in the memory


*** Version 4 ***
- added the option to set & verify maximum message size
- renamed set_message_compression() to set_compress_messages()


*** Version 3 ***
- changed compression from raw zlib to gzip (better interoperability with Java)
- network protocol refactoring
- fixed typos in comments


*** Version 2 ***
- code & network protocol refactoring


*** Version 1 ***
- initial release
